@wp.kernel
def expr_cdgtfh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v1 = wp.sin(((v0 + 0.36 / v1 + 0.77) + 0.79))
    tmp = 0.71
    v2 = ((0.12 / (v2 + 0.01 + v2 + 0.0)) - tmp)
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v0 + 0.49)) + (v0 / wp.cos(v0 + 0.0)))
    data[tid] = v0
